snippet.textDisplay: Did something change within the FBI for the PFT? I just did the hiring PFT about a year or two ago and it was way more strict and different than what she is showing. None of the situps or pushups would have counted that she did. The order of events is messed up in the video. In real life, you do Situps, 300 meter sprint, Push ups, 1.5 mile run, Pull ups. You only get 10min of rest in between each exercise. Definitely not a good representation of the entire physical test.
